== About

Currently, I am a postdoctoral researcher at [http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/ Department of Computer Science and Engineering], [http://www.cuhk.edu.hk/ The Chinese University of Hong Kong] (CUHK).
I received my Ph.D. degree from CUHK in 2025, supervised by [http://www.cse.cuhk.edu.hk/~byu/ Prof. Bei Yu].
Prior to that, I received my B.Eng. in Information Engineering at [https://www.zju.edu.cn/english/ Zhejiang University (ZJU)] in 2021.
My research interests include VLSI CAD, 3D Integrated Circuits, Machine Learning in EDA, and GPU Acceleration.

I will join the [https://sse.cuhk.edu.cn/en School of Science and Engineering] at [https://www.cuhk.edu.cn/en The Chinese University of Hong Kong, Shenzhen], as an Assistant Professor in June 2026, and I am seeking motivated M.Phil./Ph.D. students and Research Assistants with backgrounds in electronic engineering, computer science and engineering, applied mathematics, or related fields. If you are interested, please feel free to contact me by email.

== Awards

- DAC Young Fellow Award, DAC, 2025
- 3rd Place Award in CAD Contest, ICCAD, 2022
- Hong Kong PhD Fellowship, CUHK, 2021
# - First-Class Scholarship for Outstanding Merits, ZJU, 2017, 2018, 2019
